**Total missing packages: 42**

### Notes
- You already have `xorg` (meta-package) which may include `x11-utils`
- You already have `sxiv`, so `nsxiv` might be redundant
- You have PulseAudio but are considering PipeWire replacements
- You have `brightnessctl` instead of `xbacklight`
- You have `xfce4-screenshooter` instead of `maim`
